  <span class="topbar-sub">// for Java developers</span>
</div>

<div class="layout">
  <div class="sidebar">
    <div class="sidebar-section">Core Concepts</div>
    <a class="sidebar-link active" href="#what">What is Spring Boot?</a>
    <a class="sidebar-link" href="#autoconfigure">Auto-Configuration</a>
    <a class="sidebar-link" href="#starter">Starters & Dependencies</a>

